<Layout
  title="Mastotermes darwiniensis | Giant Northern Termite | Darwin Specialist | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Mastotermes darwiniensis — the Giant Northern Termite, the world's most destructive termite species and the signature Top End species. Biology, identification, why it's different from Coptotermes, and how to treat it. NT Pest Control licensed.">
  <Fragment slot="head">
